Package: Hotgenes
Type: Package
Title: For Visualizing Differential Expression Analysis
Version: 0.99.2
Author: Richard Virgen-Slane
Maintainer: The package maintainer <RVS.BioTools@gmail.com>
Description: This package reads the DESeq2 output file to provide users
    with way to visualize the results. PCA plots, DE coefficients, and 
    Heatmaps can be visualized in a web browser using this package.
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
